    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>free range</strong> <strong>chicken breast portion[s]</strong> to a clean chopping board</p><p>Slice through the thickest part of the chicken, being careful not to cut all the way through to the other side and open it out like a book</p><p>Cover with <strong>cling film</strong> and bash with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> until you have an even thickness – this is your <strong>butterflied chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1968.-step-4-x200.jpg",
