    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated chicken</strong> and cook for 4 min on each side until golden, then turn the heat down to medium and cook for a further 3-4 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Once the chicken is almost cooked add the<strong> remaining herb marinade</strong> to the pan and cook for a further 1-2 min, then once done, set aside to rest – this is your <strong>lemony free range chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
